  "texts": [
    "The conclusion of the paper is provided in \"Conclusion and future work\" section.",
    "Numerous researchers have used computer algorithms for histology image processing, and the approaches used can be divided into two categories: hand-crafted and DL techniques.",
    "The hand-crafted techniques extract features from slide images that professional pathologists would recognize.",
    "In contrast, the second category used DL techniques to automatically extract the features from the processed images.",
    "Due to their capacity to learn pertinent features directly from the raw data, Dl models, particularly CNNs, have been used more frequently in histopathology image analysis."
  ],
